        code: '// Official Example from gnolang/gno\n// Source: https://github.com/gnolang/gno/tree/master/examples/gno.land/r/archive/groups\n\npackage groups\n\nimport (\n\t"regexp"\n\n\t"gno.land/p/nt/avl"\n)\n\n//----------------------------------------\n// Realm (package) state\n\nvar (\n\tgGroups       avl.Tree // id -> *Group\n\tgGroupsCtr    int      // increments Group.id\n\tgGroupsByName avl.Tree // name -> *Group\n)\n\n//----------------------------------------\n// Constants\n\nvar reName = regexp.MustCompile(`^[a-z]+[_a-z0-9]{2,29}$`)\n',
